<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Thank You for Your Donation!</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h1 style="color: #28a745; text-align: center;">Thank You for Your Donation!</h1>
        
        <p>Dear {{ donation.firstName }} {{ donation.lastName }},</p>
        
        <p>We are grateful for your generous donation of ${{ donation.amount }}. Your support means a lot to us!</p>
        
        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
            <h3 style="color: #28a745;">Donation Details:</h3>
            <p>Amount: ${{ donation.amount }}</p>
            <p>Donation Type: {{ donation.type }}</p>
            <p>Date: {{ "now"|date("F d, Y") }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Your contribution will help make a positive impact in our community.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>Your Organization Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>